2. The apparatus of claim 1 further comprising a plurality of differential memory bit line pairs including the first memory bit line; 
a plurality of read precharge devices including the first read precharge device, a read precharge device being coupled to each memory bit line; 
a plurality of write precharge devices including the second write precharge device, a write precharge device being coupled to each memory bit line; 
a plurality of read equalization devices, a read equalization device being coupled to each differential memory bit line pair between two read precharge devices; and 
a plurality of write equalization devices, a write equalization device being coupled to each differential memory bit line pair between two write precharge devices.

16. A memory comprising: 
a memory array including a plurality of memory elements; 
a plurality of differential bit line pairs coupled to the memory array; 
a read precharge device coupled to each bit line in each differential bit line pair; and 
a write precharge device coupled to each bit line in each differential bit line pair, the write precharge devices being enabled only in response to a memory write operation.
